{
    "headline": "One Pot Chicken Pomodoro",
    "name": "One Pot Chicken Pomodoro",
    "description": "This one pot chicken pomodoro features boneless chicken, a bright, fresh-flavored tomato sauce, and pasta, cooked all in one deep skillet. It is a fabulous weeknight dish.",
